This is important.

17:11.489 --> 17:12.782
Listen.

17:12.824 --> 17:14.784
I was dancing with my old

17:12.824 --> 17:14.784
girlfriend Carrie

17:14.826 --> 17:16.327
and they played

17:14.826 --> 17:16.327
Muskrat Love, right.

17:16.369 --> 17:18.621
I had to run right out

17:16.369 --> 17:18.621
of the gym.

17:18.663 --> 17:19.956
You know, of all the songs

17:18.663 --> 17:19.956
about muskrats

17:19.998 --> 17:21.207
that one was my favorite.

17:21.248 --> 17:23.543
♪ Muskrat Suzie

17:21.248 --> 17:23.543
Muskrat Sam ♪♪

17:23.584 --> 17:26.004
Danny, please.

17:26.045 --> 17:28.255
Come on,

17:26.045 --> 17:28.255
I need your help here.

17:28.297 --> 17:32.092
I just kept thinking, what if I

17:28.297 --> 17:32.092
saw Carrie before I met Becky?

17:32.134 --> 17:34.094
You know, like, what if

17:32.134 --> 17:34.094
instead of 10-year reunions

17:34.136 --> 17:36.014
they had like

17:34.136 --> 17:36.014
7-year reunions?

17:36.055 --> 17:39.350
What if I saw her and

17:36.055 --> 17:39.350
what if I danced with her

17:39.392 --> 17:40.560
and what if I kissed her?

17:40.601 --> 17:42.144
And what if I liked it?

17:42.186 --> 17:44.397
What if Becky hears you?

17:42.186 --> 17:44.397
She's upstairs with the girls.

17:44.438 --> 17:46.858
- Becky's here?

17:44.438 --> 17:46.858
- Jess, Jess, come here.

17:46.900 --> 17:48.651
Calm down.

17:48.693 --> 17:51.905
Look, I think

17:48.693 --> 17:51.905
what you need to do

17:51.946 --> 17:53.781
is sort out your feelings

17:53.823 --> 17:56.034
like you'd sort out

17:53.823 --> 17:56.034
your laundry.

17:56.075 --> 17:57.117
Daniel.

17:57.159 --> 17:58.619
Now stay with me on this.

17:58.661 --> 18:02.415
Think of your feelings

17:58.661 --> 18:02.415
for Becky as your whites

18:02.456 --> 18:05.084
and your feelings

18:02.456 --> 18:05.084
for Carrie as your darks.

18:05.125 --> 18:06.711
Now make sure

18:05.125 --> 18:06.711
you do separate loads.

18:06.753 --> 18:08.963
Otherwise a red sock

18:06.753 --> 18:08.963
could get in with your whites

18:09.005 --> 18:10.798
and then you wind up

18:09.005 --> 18:10.798
with pink underwear.

18:13.300 --> 18:14.719
I'm sorry,

18:13.300 --> 18:14.719
these laundry analogies

18:14.761 --> 18:17.013
are highly sophisticated.

18:17.055 --> 18:20.516
Look, I think

18:17.055 --> 18:20.516
Becky's the greatest.

18:20.558 --> 18:23.185
But it's not fair for either

18:20.558 --> 18:23.185
of you to get married

18:23.227 --> 18:25.813
if you're not sure

18:23.227 --> 18:25.813
about your feelings.

18:25.855 --> 18:28.066
Whatever you need to

18:25.855 --> 18:28.066
do to sort this thing out

18:28.107 --> 18:29.400
you better do it right now.

