But, Carrie,

19:28.084 --> 19:29.836
it made me realize

19:29.877 --> 19:32.130
that everything we have

19:29.877 --> 19:32.130
is in the past.

19:34.507 --> 19:35.800
So it's really over?

19:38.094 --> 19:39.345
It's really over.

