Well, I needed to know.

19:43.057 --> 19:44.725
Me, too.

19:45.601 --> 19:47.227
Thanks for the dance.

19:48.021 --> 19:49.605
Goodbye, Jesse.

19:55.778 --> 19:57.404
Goodbye, Carrie.

20:01.659 --> 20:03.327
Becky.

