And then, get this

20:24.891 --> 20:27.185
we slow-danced

20:24.891 --> 20:27.185
to our song.

20:27.226 --> 20:28.728
Really?

20:28.769 --> 20:31.147
Yeah. And then

20:28.769 --> 20:31.147
we kissed, okay?

